@node not10 "LIST OF PLANNED FEATURES FOR TORNADO 3D 3.0"

LIST OF PLANNED FEATURES FOR @{B}TORNADO 3D 3.0@{UB}
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{B}Eyelight @{UB} have  just  revealed  the  list  of planned features for the next full
release of the 3D modeler and animation package @{B}Tornado 3D@{UB}. These are:
  * @{I}Clothes and strings @{UI}- Soft objects animation made easy.
  * @{I}Mannequins @{UI}- Male, Female and Alien characters.
  * @{I}Advanced particle systems @{UI}- Even more controllable particle systems.
  * @{I}Advanced force fields @{UI}- Completly redesigned force field system.
  * @{I}Footed Animation @{UI}- No more sliding footsteps or jumping walk-cycles.
  * @{I}Full Time Inverse Kinematics @{UI}- Always active, no need to create keyframes.
  * @{I}MeshMapping @{UI}- Deforms and fits any kind of imagery to existing meshes.
  * @{I}Flocks and Herds @{UI}- Mass-animation of semi-intelligent groups of objects.
  * @{I}Sculptor @{UI}- Clay-like shape builder and deformer.
  * @{I}3D Sound tracing @{UI}- Virtual mikes to record sounds in 3D.
  * @{I}3D Soundtrack builder @{UI}- A "surround" compatible encoder.
  * @{I}Sound  and  lip  sync @{UI} -  Define morph targets to lip-sync and tie sounds to
    actions.
  * @{I}RadMapping @{UI}- Cubic mapping technology simulates Radiosity at blazing speed.
  * @{I}Assistants @{UI}- Intelligent scripts that will automate most operations.
  * @{I}Gobos @{UI}- Shapeable light sources, also volumetric.
  * @{I}Envelopes @{UI}- For function-curve based animation.
  * @{I}Attachable  engines @{UI} -  Control  animation with noise or math other object's
    behaviour.
  * @{I}Chroma and Luma keying @{UI}- Key out unwanted backgrounds for SFX work.
  * @{I}Intensity mapping @{UI}- Match real and rendered sequences.
  * @{I}Subtractive alpha channels @{UI}- Remove non-uniformly colored backgrounds.
  * @{I}Project scheduler @{UI}- Manage projects even over a network.
  * @{I}Render engines @{UI}- Render engines for a variety of platforms.
  * @{I}2D shaper @{UI}- Full "traditional" 2D modeler, with adaptive Bezier curves.
  * @{I}N-sided polygonizator @{UI}- Concave and convex nsided polygons made easy.
  * @{I}N-sided beveler @{UI}- Bevel any combination of polygons.
  * @{I}Broadcast markers @{UI}- Broadcast Safe and Title area markers on preview.
  * @{I}Internal virtual memory @{UI}- Cuts in half rendering memory requirements.
  * @{I}P-code Golem scripts @{UI}- Faster and safe, allow plugin writers to resell their
    work.
  * @{I}Even  faster  PowerPC @{UI} -  Full  custom  math  library  and no need for 680x0
    assistance.
  * @{I}Even faster Permedia2 @{UI}- Full control over 3D chip parameters and more.
  * @{I}And much more!@{UI}

Existing  and  future  registered  @{B}Tornado3D  2.0 @{UB}users will be able to download
@{B}Tornado3D  V3.0 @{UB} for free, as part of the special "Buy @{B}Tornado3D 2.0 @{UB}get @{B}3.0 @{UB}for
free"  offer.  Upgrade price for @{B}V1.x @{UB}users that received @{B}V2.x @{UB}as a free upgrade
