@node not30 "NORDIC GLOBAL ANNOUNCES DAYTONA"

@{B}NORDIC GLOBAL @{UB}ANNOUNCES @{B}DAYTONA@{UB}
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{B}Nordic  Global @{UB} made a surprise announcement at @{B}Amiga99@{UB}--@{B}Java @{UB}for the Amiga! And
best of all, the runtime package and developer package will be FREE!

        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{I}@{B}Daytona@{UB}(®) - @{B}Java@{UB}(®) for @{B}AmigaOS@{UB}@{UI}

@{B}Daytona @{UB} is  a  complete @{B}Java 2 @{UB}runtime system for @{B}AmigaOS@{UB}, based on the "@{B}Java 2@{UB}
Platform" by @{B}Sun Microsystems, Inc. @{UB}Among other things it contains support for:
  * The complete @{B}Java 2 @{UB}API and class set, directly derived from @{B}Sun@{UB}'s reference
    implementation,  and  therefore  100%  compatible  with  the  official  @{B}Java@{UB}
    specifications  and  releases  (unlike  some  other @{B}Java @{UB}runtime engines for
    @{B}Amiga OS@{UB}).
  * Multithreading,  using a native @{B}Amiga @{UB}implementation. No @{B}Unix @{UB}emulation code
    or libraries required.
  * File and socket I/O (multithreaded) including multicasting, URL handling and
    Internet protocol engines.
  * @{B}AWT @{UB} (@{B}Abstract  Windows  Toolkit@{UB}):  The  basic  @{B}Daytona @{UB}package contains @{B}AWT@{UB}
    runtime  classes,  but  no  native  bindings @{B}AWT @{UB}bindings for native @{B}AmigaOS@{UB}
    displays are available as part of the @{B}Daytona PLUS @{UB}package.
  * @{B}JFC @{UB}(@{B}Java Foundation Classes@{UB}): @{B}Swing@{UB}, @{B}Java 2D@{UB}.
  * @{B}CORBA@{UB}

@{B}Daytona @{UB}is available FREE of charge.

        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{I}@{B}DaytonaDEV@{UB}(®)@{UI}

@{B}DaytonaDEV @{UB} is  an  add-on to @{B}Daytona@{UB}. It is intended for developers who want to
write  their own @{B}Java @{UB}programs, and compile them into @{B}Java @{UB}byte code. @{B}DaytonaDEV@{UB}
contains the following items:
  * @{B}Java @{UB}byte-code compiler: launcher and all required runtime classes.
  * Various  tools  (bytecode  disassembler,  documentation  generator,  archive
    management tools etc.)

@{B}DaytonaDEV @{UB}is available FREE of charge.

        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

@{I}@{B}Daytona PLUS@{UB}(®)@{UI}

@{B}DaytonaPLUS @{UB} is  an  independently  developed  add-on  to  @{B}Daytona @{UB}that provides
additional Amiga-specific features. @{B}DaytonaPLUS @{UB}contains:
