  * @{B}PowerPC @{UB}support for @{B}PowerUP@{UB}
  * JIT (Just-In-Time) compilers for @{B}68K @{UB}and @{B}PPC@{UB}.
  * Support  for  precompiled native (@{B}68K @{UB}and @{B}PPC@{UB}) versions of all standard @{B}Java@{UB}
