@{B}WILDFIRE 7 @{UB}- ANIMATION SEQUENCING AND 3D EFFECTS
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
@{B}Nova Design, Inc.@{UB}, producers of the award winning @{B}ImageFX @{UB}package and the highly
received @{B}Aladdin 4D @{UB}package, are proud to announce that they have arranged to be
the  exclusive distributors of the @{B}Wildfire 3D @{UB}effects package for North America
-- now in version 7!

@{B}Wildfire @{UB} is  an exciting new animation sequencing, 3D effects, transitions, and
animation  package by @{I}Andreas Maschke @{UI}published in Germany by @{B}Oberland Computer@{UB}.
It  can  be compared to @{B}SGI Flint @{UB}or @{B}Flame @{UB}systems and it is capable of creating
amazing  3D  effects  by  mapping  video  sequences  into  @{B}Wildfir@{UB}e's  intuitive
storyboard animation sequencing system.

@{B}Wildfire @{UB} is  perfect  for  the  animation hobbyist, @{B}Toaster@{UB}/@{B}Flyer @{UB}professional,
@{B}Movieshop@{UB}/@{B}Draco @{UB} editor  and  all  others who use their @{B}Amiga@{UB}s for animation and
video.

@{I}Highlights of @{B}Wildfire@{UB}@{UI}

@{B}Wildfire @{UB} is  a  professional  animation sequencer that allows you to create and
process   animations   in   several   formats,  to  generate  time-dependant  3D
special-effects  and  design  large  projects  containing several animations and
frame-synchronized  sound-effects. @{B}Wildfire@{UB}'s animation sequencing allows you to
combine animations on a timeline and output the results as a @{B}YAFA @{UB}animation with
synchronized sound.

@{B}Wildfire @{UB} is able to perform basic non-linear editing of animation sequences and
can  import  or  export frame sequences, @{B}Amiga ANIM@{UB}s, @{B}YAFA@{UB}s, @{B}MPEGs@{UB}, @{B}Windows AVI@{UB},
and @{B}Macintosh Quicktime @{UB}formats!

The  3D  effects  included  in @{B}Wildfire @{UB}include height-field deforms, cubes that
automatically  unfold  and  fold  again,  @{B}Lightwave @{UB} object  support,  3D magnet
effects,  3D transitional morphing, unlimited mathematical deformations, twists,
sphere mapping, twirling, water transitions, perspective transforms and more!
  * Full @{B}CyberGraphX @{UB}Support
  * Font Sensitive GUI
  * Full @{B}PowerPC @{UB}Support
  * Storyboard editor Interface
  * Convert using @{B}MPEG@{UB}, @{B}AVI @{UB}and @{B}Quicktime @{UB}movie formats
  * Timecodes Editor
  * Envelope Controls for Effects
  * Filmstrip Interfaces
  * Real-time Feedback
  * Transition Maker
  * Preview for almost any Operation
  * Animation with Sound
  * Post Processing Tools
  * Color correction Tools
  * 24-bit Animation Player with Sound

@{B}Wildfire @{UB}is an open development platform, like @{B}Nova Design, Inc.@{UB}'s own products,
with a complete plug-in development system and a full @{B}Arexx @{UB}interface (with over
400 commands) is included.

@{I}Ordering @{B}Wildfire@{UB}@{UI}

@{B}Wildfire @{UB} works  on your standard @{B}Amiga 68k @{UB}models as well as the @{B}PowerPC @{UB}and it
is  only  $199.95.  You'll  find it's available at your favorite @{B}Amiga @{UB}dealer or
mail order firm.

@{B}Wildfire @{UB}comes on CDROM and requires an @{B}Amiga 68k @{UB}series or @{B}PowerPC @{UB}system.
